---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="marco@web:~/about$"
  description="About Marco: engineering team lead at Entelect, and what he gets up to outside work."
  windowLabel="~/about"
  promptPath="~/about$"
  promptCmd="man marco"
  active="about"
>
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>
    I'm Marco. I lead an engineering team at Entelect, placed on
    Capitec's app team. I started at Skynamo, then moved to
    Entelect on a team at Standard Bank, where I grew into
    leading it.
  </p>
  <p>
    I care more about honest feedback than comfortable silence.
    Growing people, not just managing their tasks.
  </p>
  <p>
    Outside work I spend most of my time with my wife and our
    dogs. The rest goes to side projects in Rust and Odin,
    digital art (no AI), and Magic: The Gathering.
  </p>
  <p>
    This site is where I put projects, books I'm reading, and
    the occasional post.
  </p>

  <h2>stack</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Languages: Rust, Odin, TypeScript, C#, Java, Golang</li>
    <li>Tools: Neovim, Git, GitHub, Kafka, Kubernetes, Docker, Azure, AWS</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
